"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-01-09-mary-lou-retton-says-she-faced-death-in-eyes-during-ordeal-with-pneumonia\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Legendary U.S. gymnast Mary Lou Retton said she faced \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cdeath in the eyes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d during a battle with pneumonia that required hospitalization in the intensive care unit in the fall.\\u00c2  The 1984 gold medalist shared her experience dealing with a life-threatening illness in her first public interview with NBC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099sToday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_Retton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mary Lou Retton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_Retton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_Retton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many questions remain about Retton\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s health condition and financial situation, and she didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t provide much detail to Today\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Hoda Kotb.\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she made it clearhow grave her situation was.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis is serious and this is life and I am so grateful to be here,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Retton told Kotb from her home outside San Antonio.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"score\": 0.9229401131486661, \"rank\": 0.0767195912600178, \"text\": \"Antonio\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonio_Lopez-Fitzgerald\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI am blessed to be here because there is a time when they were about to put me on life support.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Making Retton\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hospitalization even more harrowing were financial circumstances that left her unable to cover medical expenses.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had no health insurance, which compelled her family to request donations through online crowdfunding sites.\\u00c2  Legendary Olympic gymnast Mary Lou Retton speaks exclusively to@hodakotbabout the fight for her life with a rare form of pneumonia that landed her in the ICU for a month and the outpouring support from her fans.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_Retton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mary Lou Retton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_Retton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Lou_Retton\"}, {\"begin\": 1134, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intensive_care_unit\", \"score\": 0.9990620653035234, \"rank\": 0.0009388152434239947, \"text\": \"ICU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intensive_care_unit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intensive_care_unit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI have so much to look forward to.\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m a fighter.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dpic.twitter.com/WiYj2BKbIl  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t afford it, I couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t afford it, I couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t afford it,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Retton said.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut who would even know that this was going to happen to me?\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the bottom line, I couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t afford it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Thanks to nearly\\u00c2\\u00a0$459,000 raised through donations, Retton says her expenses are \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009call set now\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and her daughter McKenna KelleytoldUSA Todaythat the remaining funds would be donated to charity.\\u00c2  Retton was the first American woman to win a gold medal in the individual all-around competition at the 1984 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"score\": 0.9999999990127435, \"rank\": 5.281178493507161e-10, \"text\": \"American woman\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also won two silver and two bronze medals at the Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999675897021, \"rank\": 3.08237879656712e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her achievements resulted in winningSports Illustrated\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099sSportswoman of the Year.\\u00c2  Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations    \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": []}, {